        "text":" \n______________________________________________________________\n| : : : : : : : : : : : : : : : :_________________________: : : : : : : : : : : : : : : : : |\n| : : : : : : : : : : : : : )_ :      POHCHENG JEWELS      : _( : : : : : : : : : : : : : : |\n| : : : : : : : : : : : : : : : :---------------------------------------: : : : : : : : : : : : : : : : :|\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\n| : : :| ______    _  .'                                                         '.  _    ______   |: : : |\n|==  | .' ,|,  '. /_\\  |                             ----|----                            |  /_\\ .'  ,|, '. |  ==|\n|      | | ;;;;;  | =|= |                           |      |      |                          | =|= |  ;;;;; | |      |\n|      | |_';;;'_|                                   |  __|__  |                                  |_';;;'_| |      |\n|      |                   |                          |       |       |                          |                |      |\n|      |                   |                          |       |       |                          |                |      |\n|___ |_________|                          |       |       |                          |________| ___|\n\nOn the sides are stretches of the typical shops you find in a shopping \ncentre. The exit signs emit a green glow in the dark. \n\nThe toy store looked the busiest, with shelves of intricate toy models \nand video game consoles on display. \n\nA few shopfronts down is the jewellery shop. Other than the few \nadvertisement wallpapers, pretty much everything on display were \ncovered up with black cloth.\n\nAt the far end lies an altar that glows dim red, where the more religious\nChinese shop owners pray for good prosperity. The incense sticks had \nstopped burning, but its smoky scent still lingered along the walkway.\n\n\n(To Level 1)--------------------------------------------------------(To Level 3)\n\n===================================================\n||     Clipboard     ||     Torchlight     ||                Walkie-Talkie                ||\n===================================================",
